SUMMARY:Meet the Maker: Robert Foley Vineyards Session I
LOCATION:The Living Room
DESCRIPTION:Category: Food & Beverage\nPrice: Free\nStatus: Waitlist Only\n
 Event URL: https://members.thequinhouse.com/events/175770\n\nJoin us for a
 n intimate afternoon with Robert Foley of Robert Foley Wines\, one of Napa
  Valley’s most revered vintners. With decades of winemaking expertise\, 
 Robert’s approach is rooted in precision\, patience\, and a deep respect
  for the vineyard. Each varietal reflects the distinct expression of its t
 erroir—structured\, layered\, and built to age—while remaining unmista
 kably expressive in the glass. Throughout the tasting\, members will explo
 re aroma\, structure\, and nuance in an interactive dialogue designed to s
 harpen the senses and deepen appreciation.\n\nRobert will personally guide
  members through a curated tasting of five exceptional wines—Charbono 20
 21\, Chardonnay 2023\, Claret 2018\, Griffin 2019\, and Napa Cabernet 2018
 —offering insight into the craft\, character\, and philosophy behind eac
 h bottle.\n\n*This event is complimentary and reserved for members only. L
 ight bites will be served.
URL:https://members.thequinhouse.com/events/175770
CATEGORIES:Food & Beverage
END:VEVENT
