SUMMARY:Hands-On Impact: Wonderfund's Period Party
LOCATION:Offsite: Roadrunner
DESCRIPTION:Category: ‘Quin Impact Fund\nPrice: Free\nAvailability: 20 sp
 ots left\nStatus: Available\nEvent URL: https://members.thequinhouse.com/e
 vents/176383\n\nJoin The ‘Quin Impact Fund for the fourth annual Period 
 Party\, hosted by The Wonderfund at Roadrunner\, which brings together wom
 en from across Greater Boston to celebrate their roles as leaders\, philan
 thropists\, and changemakers - while making a tangible difference for teen
 s engaged with the Massachusetts Department of Children and Families. \n\n
 During this high-energy volunteer event\, more than 500 participants will 
 come together to assemble 10\,000 menstrual hygiene kits\, ensuring young 
 people across the Commonwealth have reliable access to essential menstrual
  products. These kits will be distributed to all 29 DCF area offices\, whe
 re social workers can provide them directly to the teens they support. Las
 t year’s effort packed and distributed more than 13\,000 kits - be a par
 t of helping to do it again. \n\n*This event is complimentary and reserved
  for members only.
URL:https://members.thequinhouse.com/events/176383
CATEGORIES:‘Quin Impact Fund
END:VEVENT
