SUMMARY:Art Tour: Celebrating Female Artists
LOCATION:Meet in The Lobby
DESCRIPTION:Category: The Arts\nPrice: Free\nStatus: Waitlist Only\nEvent U
 RL: https://members.thequinhouse.com/events/173809\n\nlease join The 'Quin
  House Art Collection curator Kate Chertavian for an art tour in celebrati
 on of Women's History Month that will journey throughout the 'House. We wi
 ll gather in the Lobby for a deep dive on works by Julie Mehretu\, Zainab 
 Sumu\, and Louise Nevelson. Then tour highlights by female artists in the 
 Reading Room\, up the grand staircase\, and conclude in Bondo with an expl
 oration of Candida Höfer's magnificent photographs.\n\n*This event is com
 plimentary and reserved for members\, plus one guest.
