  against the Atlantic Hawks.\n\nAll suite ticket options include incredibl
 e views of the on-court action and light game day bites. Quench your eveni
 ng cravings with a grazing spread of cheese & charcuterie\, mezze\, jumbo 
 shrimp cocktail and seasonal snacks! The suite also offers an assortment o
 f refreshments including wine\, beer\, seltzer and soft drinks. Are you ga
 me?\n\n*A pair of 'Quin suite seats is available for $941 total ($470.50 p
 er ticket). Individual suite tickets are available for bar stool / standin
 g access only\, offered at a reduced price of $433 per ticket. Suite ticke
 ts are non-refundable and are non-transferable. Members may purchase ticke
 ts for up to 3 guests and are required to accompany them at all times. The
