SUMMARY:Live Music: Zahili Zamora
LOCATION:The Reading Room
DESCRIPTION:Category: The Arts\nPrice: Free / Included\nStatus: Available\n
 Event URL: https://members.thequinhouse.com/events/177696\n\nExperience th
 e dynamic artistry of Zahili Gonzalez Zamora\, a Cuban-born pianist\, comp
 oser\, and bandleader whose sound is rooted in tradition and propelled by 
 bold improvisation. Classically trained and shaped by a journey that has t
 aken her from Cuba to Canada\, Southeast Asia\, and now the United States\
 , Zahili brings depth\, movement\, and unmistakable vitality to modern Lat
 in jazz.\n\nExpect driving rhythms\, masterful spontaneity\, and a perform
 ance that feels both deeply personal and exhilaratingly alive. Settle in\,
  sip something spirited from the neighboring Little Bar\, and let her musi
 c carry you.\n\n*This event is complimentary and available to members\, pl
 us three guests. Seating is first come\, first served.
URL:https://members.thequinhouse.com/events/177696
CATEGORIES:The Arts
