LOCATION:Meet in The Lobby
DESCRIPTION:Category: The Arts\nPrice: Free\nAvailability: 4 spots left\nSt
 atus: Available\nEvent URL: https://members.thequinhouse.com/events/176378
 \n\nJoin ‘Quin Art Collection Curator\, Kate Chertavian for a historical
 ly focused tour exploring the “Old Boys” of the ’Quin. Featured high
 lights include Edmund Charles Tarbell’s Portrait of President Calvin Coo
 lidge (1927) and Édouard Detaille’s Soldier on Horseback (1889)\, both 
 on view in the historic Reading Room.\n\nThe conversation continues along 
 the Grand Staircase\, where Kate will share insights into the curatorial p
 rocess and the thoughtful dialogue between historical and contemporary wor
 ks woven throughout the collection.\n\n*This event is complimentary and re
 served for members\, plus one registered guest.
